    "title": "ASAS Criteria for Peripheral SpondyloArthritis (SpA)",
    "desc": "The ASAS Criteria for Peripheral SpondyloArthritis (SpA) diagnoses peripheral spondyloarthritis in patients presenting with peripheral arthritis, enthesitis and/or dactylitis.",
